{"tid":1591904,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"10.1 係要遍地開花先係真正升級。 請幫share","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T19:21:30.000Z","uid":88306,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72a7ffd1b724214294f637abd26f69f63d366d7a","tid":1591904,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"首先。。。我唔敢講我係前線，我只能夠講我係前中遊既一樣睇法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q :十月一出去集中去港島，有咩好處？最後結果係點？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A: 最後結果咪又係同狗對峙同被圍捕。所以我地應該要遍地開花，分散警力，<br />\n起碼前線揹住成袋full gear都唔駛驚有road block.走又唔駛咁擔驚受怕啦。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q: 點解人多集中先會有更多媒體關注？</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">[red]呢個係on9既睇法，其實遍地開花一樣做到同樣效果。媒體報導唔會因爲人多先有關注，<br />\n只要更多人更勇武，更加升級就會有更多人關注。<br />\n所以唔好用守舊諗法去局限自己思想  </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日大家講到明<span style=\"color: red;\">831</span> 為死線，再不回應就全民升級，結果升左去邊？<br />\n<br />\n升到依家先慢慢有人接受到火魔法咋。 <br />\n獅鳥仲有班和理非屌緊我地暴力 <br />\n<br />\n明明好耐之前講到明10月1要真正升級，<br />\n賀佢老母国慶。<br />\n<br />\n依家風向又吹10月1留力要和平？<br />\n<br />\n你地當前線係咩撚野？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後：<br />\n認同請正評&amp;分享</span>"},{"pid":"9800e41384d713a34db4feab38f7278e54cb907b","tid":1591904,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"f494de3da485671a37b171f79a10a9eb2d8c8107","tid":1591904,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a28b19288f63ea4a1dd265aa06692462100bee3f","tid":1591904,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"點撚解無人睇"},{"pid":"ac59dc32c01c19fff6c64354a9329c30bbcdf74d","tid":1591904,"uid":88306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"cfa30e8ad998082b17cf6544cda915b42cec4141","tid":1591904,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"遍地開花會變左全港主流民意係反政府"},{"pid":"2b9391124d60beb69420fe811ac2ab301bb31ddc","tid":1591904,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:21:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>Tg channel 在此 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=6a7bc282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> <span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>"},{"pid":"923aea3c4bdba2978836c141a139796e52f921c2","tid":1591904,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T19:21:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做得忍者，一定要識保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjzvXH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjzvXH8.jpg&h=b6574070&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}